'Yan majalisar dokokin Wales sun ji tsoron a kira su 'yan damfara
Wasu 'yan majalisar sun yi takaici, sakamakon wani shiri na sauya sunansu zuwa 'yan majalisar dokokin kasar Wales (Member of the Welsh Parliament, MWP).
An samo ra'ayin ne daga shirin sake suna majalisa zuwa majalisar dokokin Wales.
'Yan majalisa daga kowane bangare na siyasa suna fargabar cewa za a yi musu ba'a.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Labour ya nuna damuwa game da kungiyarsa, yana mai cewa sabon sunan yana yin waƙa da kalmomin Welsh twp da pwp.
Ga masu karatu daga waje: a harshen Welsh kalmar twp tana nufin wawa, kuma kalmar pwp  ita ce ƙazanta.
Wani dan siyasa na jam'iyyar Plaid Cymru ya ce jam'iyyarsa ba ta "farin ciki" da shawarar ba, kuma ya gabatar da wasu hanyoyin magance matsalar.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Conservative Party ta Wales ya ce jam'iyyarsa ta auki niyyar sauya sunan, amma ya lura cewa kalmar MWP tana da kama da kalmar muppet.
A wannan yanayin, ana furta haruffan Welsh w kamar yadda ake furta u a yaren Turanci na Yorkshire.
Kwamitin da ke aiki a cikin taron, wanda ke aiki a kan tsarin dokar da ke sauya sunan, ya ɗauki wannan matsayin: Tabbas, yanke shawara ta ƙarshe game da taken membobin taron zai kasance a kansu.
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba wa Majalisar Tarayyar Wales damar canza sunanta.
A watan Yuni, kwamitin ya wallafa sakamakon taron jama'a kan wannan tsari.An samu goyon baya sosai ga sauya majalisa zuwa majalisar dokokin kasar Wales.
Bugu da ƙari, kwamitin ya goyi bayan shawarar sauya sunan membobin majalisa zuwa Mambobin Majalisar Wales, ko WMP a Turanci, kodayake ƙanƙantar MWP ce ta fi shahara a cikin jama'a.
'Yan majalisa na gabatar da wasu hanyoyin da za a bi, kuma wahalar samun yarjejeniya ta zama abin damuwa ga Elin Jones, shugabar majalisa, wacce za ta gabatar da dokar a cikin makonni masu zuwa.
Dokar da ke kawo sauyi za ta kuma yi la'akari da wasu canje-canje a yadda ake gudanar da taron, ciki har da ƙa'idodin janyewar mambobi da tsarin tsarin kwamitin.
'Yan majalisar za su iya zabar sunayensu na gaba yayin da za a tattauna dokar.
'Yan Macedonia sun kada kuri'ar raba gardama kan sauya sunan kasar
A ranar Lahadi mai zuwa, masu kada kuri'a za su yanke shawara ko ƙasarsu za ta zama Jamhuriyar Arewacin Macedonia nan ba da jimawa ba.
An yi wannan zabe ne domin kawo karshen takaddama da aka shafe shekaru ana yi da kasar Girka da ke makwabtaka da ita, inda ake samun yankin da ake kira Macedonia.
Gwamnatin Athens ta daɗe tana da'awar cewa sunan makwabciyarta ta arewa tana da'awar ƙasa, kuma ta yi ta hamayya da ƙoƙarin shiga Tarayyar Turai da NATO.
George Ivanov, shugaban kasar Macedonia kuma mai adawa da zaben raba gardama kan sauya sunan kasar, ya ce zai yi watsi da sakamakon zaben.
Amma masu goyon bayan zaben, ciki har da firaministan kasar Zoran Zaew, sun ce canjin ya zama dole domin kasar ta samu shiga Tarayyar Turai da NATO.
An daina kiran coci a New York City domin matsalolin da ake fuskanta a majami'u a Harlem
"Masu girma da na yi magana da su sun ce a dā akwai mashaya da coci a kowane kusurwa".
"A yanzu babu inda aka same su".
Kamar yadda ya ce, babu shakka, babu abin da ya sa ba a taɓa samun mashaya a duniya ba.
"Yanzu mutane suna yin tarayya a wasu hanyoyi", in ji shi.
Bars ba su zama wurin taro na yau da kullum na membobin al'umma ba.
A batun majami'u, yana damuwa cewa kuɗin da aka samu daga sayar da dukiyar ba zai isa ba har tsawon lokacin da masu yin wannan zaɓin suke tsammani, kuma cewa 'da wuri ko daga baya za su isa wurin da suka fara' ba.
Ya ce za a iya maye gurbin majami'u da gidajen da mutane suke zama, waɗanda ba za su tallafa wa sauran majami'u da ke kusa ba.
Kamar yadda ya ce: "Mafi yawan mutanen da suke sayen gidaje a irin wannan gini za su kasance fararen fata, kuma hakan zai hanzarta rufe majami'u gaba daya, domin ba za a iya samun sabbin mazauna a cikin majami'u ba".
Ikilisiyoyin biyu sun kasance da taron masu imani na fararen fata kafin Harlem ta shiga cikin babban birni a 1870 (cocin St. Martin ya shiga cikin al'umma shekaru goma bayan haka).
Taron farko na fararen Methodist sun bar yankin a shekarun 1930.
Sai wani taron jama'ar Afirka suka karɓi ikon mallakar ginin.
Ikilisiyar St. Martin ta karbe ta ne daga taron jama'a karkashin jagorancin Reverend John Howard Johnson, wanda ya jagoranci boycott kan dillalai na 125th Street (babban hanyar kasuwanci a Harlem) da ke adawa da daukar aiki ko inganta 'yan Afirka.
Wutar 1939 ta lalata ginin sosai, amma masu wa'azi na John Howard Johnson sun yi shirye-shiryen sake gina haikalin kuma sun ba da umarnin gina ƙungiyar karrarawa.
Reverend David Johnson, ɗan John Howard Johnson kuma magajinsa a St. Martin's Church, ya yi alfahari da kiran sabon karilyona "Kwanon talakawa".
Wani masani wanda ya yi kira a watan Yuli ya bayyana su a wasu hanyoyi dabam, a matsayin "dukiya ta al'adu" da kuma "kayan tarihi mara canji".
Tiffany Ng, ƙwararren masanin ilimin lissafi a Jami'ar Michigan, ta kuma lura cewa wannan ne karillon na farko da ɗan rawa mai launin fata ya yi, wanda Dionisio A. Lind ya yi, wanda ya koma coci na Riverside Church shekaru 18 da suka gabata, inda ya sami babban ƙungiyar mawaƙa.
Malcolm J. Merriweather ya ce St. Martin ba ya maye gurbinsa.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, an samu wasu abubuwa masu rikitarwa a cocin St. Martin da suka shafi gine-gine da masu yin gine-gine, wasu daga cikinsu shugabannin cocin ne suka kawo su, wasu kuma daga cocin Episcopal.
A watan Yuli, kwamitin parish (gwamnatin da ke kula da ikilisiya da ke da shugabannin addini) ya mayar da hankalinsa ga diocese, yana mai cewa yana son ya tura kudaden zuwa kwamitin, ko da yake kwamitin bai shiga cikin hayar gine-ginen da masu aikin gini da aka tura ba.
Wasu 'yan majami'a kuma sun koka game da rashin nuna gaskiya a cikin diocese.
