Peter Jones ya yi fushi bayan Holly Willoughby ta janye daga kwangilarsa ta fam miliyan 11.
Peter Jones, tauraron wasan kwaikwayon Dragons Den, ya yi fushi da jin cewa Holly Willoughby zai yi murabus daga kamfanin sayar da kayayyaki mai darajar fam miliyan 11 domin mayar da hankali kan sabuwar hadin gwiwa da Marks da Spencer da ITV
Holly Willoughby ba ta da lokaci don alamar kayan haɗi da kayan gida da ake kira Truly.
An gwada ayyukansa da Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop a lokutan da yawa.
A safiyar yau, mai gabatar da shirye-shiryen mai shekaru 37 ta sanar da murabus ta hanyar Instagram.
Yanke shawara na kwatsam na barin ingantacciyar hanyar rayuwa da mayar da hankali kan sabon haɗin gwiwa tare da Marks & Spencer da ITV da Holly Willoughby ya yi ya fusata Peter Jones, tauraron Dragons Den.
Kamar yadda majiya ta ruwaito, Peter Jones ya yi fushi lokacin da wata sananniyar mai gabatar da shirye-shiryen talabijin ta sanar a wani taron tashin hankali a ranar Talata a hedkwatar mulkinsa na kasuwanci a Marlow, Buckinghamshire, cewa saboda sabbin kwangila har zuwa fam miliyan 1.5 ba za ta sami lokacin sadaukar da kanta ga alamarsu ta kayan haɗi da kayan gida Truly ba.
An kwatanta kamfanin da Gwyneth Paltrow ta mallaka, Goop, kuma an ce za ta ninka dukiyar Holly Willoughby da aka kiyasta ya kai fam miliyan 11.
Bayan da Holly Willoughby, mai shekara 37, ta sanar da barin Truly a shafin Instagram, sai Peter Jones ya bar Burtaniya, inda ya tafi daya daga cikin gidajen hutu.
Kamar yadda majiya ta ruwaito, Mark Truly ya kasance babban fifiko ga Holly Willoughby.
Ta yi alkawarin cewa za ta yi amfani da ita a nan gaba kuma za ta yi hakan har shekaru masu zuwa.
