Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Amurka ta ba da gargadin cewa za a iya samun ambaliyar ruwa a yammacin Arizona, kudancin Nevada da gabashin California da Utah a ranar Litinin da Talata, ciki har da Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City.
