Bayan haka, za ta haye Mexico ta nufi arewacin ƙasar a matsayin guguwa, kuma za ta kai iyakar jihar Arizona a matsayin guguwa a ranar Talata da safe, kuma za ta kai kudancin Utah a ranar Talata da yamma.
