Dan wasan mai shekaru 56 yana taka rawar Jack Jarvis a cikin shahararren shirin BBC, yana nunawa kuma yana samar da shirin tare da abokin aikinsa na shekaru da yawa, Greg Hemphill.
Duet ya sanar cewa kakar wasa ta tara da ke tafe ita ce ta karshe a tarihin wasan kwaikwayon, kuma duk wani abin da ke nuna cewa Ford Kiernan yana shirin makomar sa bayan ya bar Craigslist.
A cewar hukuma, ya zama darakta na kamfanin Adriftmorn Limited.
