Tauraruwar Game of Thrones Kit Harington ya yi magana game da cutarwa mai guba
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin HBO na wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones.
Dan wasan mai shekaru 31 ya yi watsi da akidar jarumin, yana mai cewa nuna irin wadannan halayen a kan allo na sa matasa maza su yi tunanin cewa dole ne su yi wasan tsattsauran ra'ayi don a girmama su.
A cikin hira da jaridar Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce wani abu ya faru da shi, kuma yana tunanin yadda za a magance matsalar cutarwa ta maza a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri abokin aikinsa na Game of Thrones, mai shekaru 31 mai suna Rose Leslie, ya ce yana jin "tabbatacce" da ya kawo wannan batun.
"Ni kaina ina jin daɗi sosai a wannan lokacin" "a ina muka yi kuskure game da namiji?" "ya ce.
Me muka koya wa maza yayin da suke girma, idan muka duba su daga mahangar matsalar da muke fuskanta a yau?
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama wani ɓangare na ci gaban ƙwayoyin cuta na maza saboda nuna halayen maza.
Ya ci gaba: "Waɗanne halaye ne aka haifa, kuma waɗanne ne aka koya?
Menene ake koya wa yara a talabijin da kuma a kan titi da ke sa matasa maza su soma tunanin cewa dole ne su tsaya a wani bangare domin su zama maza?
Ina tsammanin wannan shine ɗayan mahimman batutuwan zamaninmu  menene za a iya yi don canza shi?
A bayyane yake cewa ba kome ba ne mai kyau game da matasa maza.
Ya kuma bayyana a cikin hirar cewa ba zai sake yin wani abu ba a cikin prequel ko sequel na Game of Thrones bayan wasan ya ƙare a shekara mai zuwa, yana mai cewa ya "ƙare daga fagen fama da dawakai".
Daga watan Nuwamba, Kit zai yi fim din Sam Shepard mai suna True West, wanda ke ba da labarin wani mai samar da fim da ɗan'uwansa ɓarawo.
A kwanan nan, ɗan wasan ya bayyana cewa ya ga cewa saduwa da matarsa Rose shine mafi kyawun abin da ya taɓa faruwa da shi a Game of Thrones.
"A kan allon na sadu da matata, wanda ya ba ni sabuwar iyali da kuma sabuwar rayuwa", in ji shi.
A cikin wannan lambar yabo ta Emmy Award-winning fantasy series, Rose ta taka rawar Ygritte  wanda ke da sha'awar ƙaunar mutumin da Kit ya buga, Jon Snow.
Ma'auratan sun yi aure a watan Yunin 2018 a gidan Leslie a Scotland.
HIV/AIDS: Kasar Sin ta samu karuwar sabbin kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14 cikin 100
Kasar Sin ta sanar da cewa yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da kuma masu fama da cutar AIDS ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
A ƙasar, fiye da mutane 820,000 ne suke fama da wannan matsalar, in ji ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya.
A cikin kwata na biyu na shekarar 2018 kadai, an samu sabbin mutane kusan 40,000.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun kasance ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya nuna canji daga baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin ta hanyar kamuwa da jini.
Amma, an rage yawan masu kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar, kamar yadda jami'an lafiya na kasar Sin suka fada a wani taron da aka gudanar a lardin Yunnan.
Amma a shekara guda, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da kuma cutar AIDS a China ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma nuna bambanci ga mutanen LGBT ya zama ruwan dare gama gari.
Idan aka yi la'akari da dabi'u na gargajiya na kasar, bincike ya kiyasta cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90% na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza za su yi aure da mata.
Yawancin mutane suna kamuwa da cutar ne saboda rashin kāriya a lokacin jima'i.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta samar da maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani daga cikin tawagarta ya bayyana bayanan 'yan majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican.
A ranar Asabar, 'Yar Majalisar Wakilai ta Amurka, Maxine Waters, ta yi watsi da zargin cewa wani daga cikin tawagarta ya sanya bayanan sirri na 'yan majalisa uku na Republican a shafukan Wikipedia na masu yin dokar.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Democrat na Los Angeles ya tabbatar da cewa, masana da shafukan yanar gizo masu alaka da 'yan tsattsauran ra'ayi ne suka kawo wannan zargi.
Waters ta sanar a cikin wata sanarwa a shafinta na Twitter cewa, "karya, karya, da kuma karin karya".
An ce bayanan da aka fitar sun ƙunshi adireshin gida da kuma lambobin waya na 'yan majalisar dattawa Lindsey Graham na jihar South Carolina da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch na Utah.
Wani mutum da ba a san shi ba ne ya wallafa wannan labarin a ranar Alhamis a fadar shugaban kasa a lokacin da ake sauraron karar da aka yi wa wanda aka naɗa a matsayin babban alkalin kotun tarayya, wato Brett Kavanaugh, game da zargin da ake yi masa na yin lalata da mata.
Wannan bayanan ya fito ne bayan wasu 'yan majalisar dattijai uku sun kalubalanci Kavanaugh.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ba da rahoton cewa adireshin IP da ke gano asalin post ɗin ya danganta da ofishin Waters kuma sun buga bayanan game da memba na ƙungiyar Waters  kamar yadda Hill ya ce.
Waters ta ci gaba da cewa, "Wannan zargi na rashin tushe ba gaskiya ba ne kuma karya ne kashi dari bisa dari".
Mambobin tawagar wanda aka keta sunansa, bayanansa da kuma tsaronsa sakamakon wadannan zarge-zargen na yaudara da karya ba su da alhakin wannan bayanan da aka fitar.
Wannan zargi na rashin tushe ba gaskiya ba ne kuma karya ne kashi ɗari bisa ɗari.
Sanarwar Waters ta jawo suka a yanar gizo, ciki har da na Ari Fleischer  tsohon kakakin fadar White House.
"Wannan hanyar ƙin yarda ba ta da kyau", in ji Fleischer.
Wannan ya nuna cewa ba ta da halin da ya dace ta zama 'yar majalisa.
Idan aka zargi mutum da abin da bai yi ba, ba zai iya zama mugun ba.
Ba za ta iya yin hakan ba.
Ba za ta iya ƙin ƙalubalanci dalilin da ya sa ake zarginsa ba.
Amma dole ne ya kasance mai natsuwa.
Fleischer ya bayyana cewa yana kwatanta yadda Waters ya amsa da sukar da 'yan Democrat suka yi wa mai shari'a Kavanaugh, wanda aka zargi da nuna fushi a lokacin sauraron ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican da ke takarar zaben tsakiyar shekara na shekara ta 2016 don maye gurbin Waters, ya kuma bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafinsa na Twitter.
"Abubuwa masu ban tsoro idan gaskiya ne", in ji shi a shafinsa na Twitter.
Waters ta ce a cikin sanarwar ta ofishinta ta sanar da "hukumomi da hukumomin da suka dace game da zargin da ake yi na yaudara".
"Za a fallasa masu tuhumar kuma a hukunta su saboda duk wani abin da suka yi wanda zai iya zama barazana ga kowane memba na tawagar", in ji ta.
