Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan yaki da sabon tsarin ba da mafaka
Jihohi 18 da kuma Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan ƙalubalen doka game da sabuwar manufar Amurka ta hana ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke gudu daga ƙungiyoyi ko kuma tashin hankali na cikin gida.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da na gundumar sun gabatar da wata takarda ta amicus curiae a Washington a ranar Juma'a don tallafawa mai neman mafaka da ke fama da wannan manufa  kamar yadda NBC News ta ruwaito.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan wanda ke da'awar a shari'ar Grace v. Sessions da kungiyar American Civil Liberties Union ta shigar a watan Agusta kan dokar tarayya ba.
Ta ce abokin aikinta da 'ya'yansa maza masu cin zarafin 'yan kungiyar sun yi mata fyade, amma jami'an Amurka sun ki amincewa da neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga watan Yuli.
