Masu gabatar da kara na jihohin da ke goyon bayan Grace sun kwatanta El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, da suke da yawan masu neman mafaka a Amirka, a matsayin ƙasashe da ke fama da matsalar 'yan bindiga da kuma tashin hankali a gida.
Sabuwar manufar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta soke shawarar da Hukumar Daukaka Kararraki ta Shige da Fice ta yi a shekarar 2014 da ta bai wa baƙi marasa tushe damar neman mafaka domin tserewa daga cin zarafin cikin gida.
Karl Racine, babban lauyan kotun gundumar Columbia, ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar ta "yi watsi da dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na kasa da kasa" da suka dade suna aiki.
"Dokar tarayya ta bukaci a yi la'akari da duk wani neman mafaka bisa ga takamaiman gaskiya da kuma yanayi, kuma irin wannan haramcin ya saba wa wannan ka'ida", kamar yadda aka rubuta a cikin amicus curiæ.
Masu gabatar da kara sun kara da cewa, dokar hana baƙi shiga tana cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna mai cewa, baƙi za su iya zama 'yan kasuwa kuma su samar da aikin yi.
A watan Yuni ne babban lauyan shari'a Jeff Sessions ya umarci alƙalan 'yan gudun hijira su daina ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke gudun gudun hijira daga tashin hankali na gida da na 'yan bindiga.
