Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin amfani da tallace-tallace na farfaganda.
Mako guda bayan da jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani tallan shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke yabon amfanin da ake samu daga cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
A ranar Laraba, shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a kan shafin China Daily a cikin Des Moines Register  jaridar da ta fi kowa samun tallafi a jihar Iowa  yana zargin China da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben da za a yi na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba  China ta musanta wannan zargi.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Beijing ta yi kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya tabbatar da abin da jami'an Amurka suka fada wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters cewa wani sabon mataki ne na kara matsin lamba a kan kasar Sin.
Yayin da ya zama al'ada gwamnatocin kasashen waje su sanya tallace-tallace da ke inganta kasuwanci da ƙasashensu, Beijing da Washington suna ci gaba da faɗaɗa yaƙin cinikayya wanda ya kai ga ɗaga haraji a kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa da su.
An yi niyyar cewa takunkumin da China ta yi a farkon yakin cinikayya zai shafi masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa, wadanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump , in ji masana na China da na Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan jihar Iowa mai shekaru da yawa, "babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin", ya ce Beijing ta yi wa ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da 'yan kasuwa illa.
Branstad ya ce a cikin wata kasida a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register ta ranar Lahadi, cewa China ta "ƙara ƙarfinta" ta fara zalunci ta hanyar sanya tallace-tallace na farfaganda a cikin 'yan jaridarmu masu 'yanci.
"A cikin yada farfagandarsu, gwamnatin China tana amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin magana da kuma 'yancin jarida ta hanyar sanya tallace-tallace na biya a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
Amma a wani rumfar da ke kan titi a birnin Beijing, ba za ka ga muryoyin adawa ba, kuma ba za ka ga ainihin ra'ayoyin da 'yan kasar Sin ke da su game da yanayin tattalin arzikin da kasar Sin ke bi ba, saboda ana sarrafa kafofin watsa labarai sosai a karkashin jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin.
Ya kara da cewa, "daya daga cikin manyan jaridun kasar Sin ta ki buga" labarin nasa, duk da cewa bai ce wacce jaridar ba.
'Yan Republican sun yi ta cin amanar juna a zaben da aka yi na tsakiyar shekara, saboda batun Kavanaugh, manazarta sun yi gargadin
Yayin da manyan 'yan jam'iyyar Republican ke goyon bayan da kuma kare wanda aka nada a matsayin mai shari'a a kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh a fuskar zargin da ake yi masa na cin zarafin mata, wani manazarci ya yi gargadin cewa 'yan jam'iyyar za su fuskanci mummunan martani a lokacin zaben da ke tafe, musamman daga mata.
An samu karbuwa sosai a wannan taron, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun amince su yi zabe.
"Ba za a iya sake dawo da wannan ba", in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell a Jami'ar Syracuse, a wata kasida da aka wallafa a ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya ce yana da shakku kan ko kokarin da Sanata Jeff Flake (Arizona) ya yi na gudanar da bincike na minti na karshe da FBI zai isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba, ba za su manta da shi gobe ba, kuma ba za su manta da shi ba har zuwa watan Nuwamba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma kakakin kungiyar masu ci gaba ta MoveOn, a ranar Juma'a, kamar yadda jaridar Washington ta ruwaito.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a masu zanga-zanga sun yi ta ihu suna cewa "Nuwamba na zuwa", suna zanga-zanga a zauren majalisar dattawa saboda yanke shawarar da 'yan Republican suka yi na jan ragamar kwamitin shari'a na kada kuri'ar Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, kamar yadda Mic ya ruwaito.
"Abin da ya faru a kasar nan ya nuna cewa, akwai gagarumar sha'awar dimokradiyya", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai sharhi kan siyasa.
"Mutane suna cewa ya riga ya yi tsayi, kuma gaskiya ne.
Amma za a iya samun mafi girma, musamman a tsakanin mata masu ra'ayin mazan jiya da ke zaune a unguwannin gari da kuma matasa masu zaɓe masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda ko da yake ba sa son shugaban ƙasa, sau da yawa ba sa jefa ƙuri'a.
Tun kafin Ford ta yi shaida a fili inda ta bayyana dalla-dalla zargin da ta yi na cin zarafin wani dan takarar kotun koli, manazarta sun nuna cewa idan 'yan Republican suka amince da takarar, za a iya samun gagarumar amsa.
"Jam'iyyar Republican ta fuskanci matsala", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National, a farkon makon da ya gabata, kamar yadda NBC News ta ruwaito.
"Ba wai kawai batun zaben kwamitin ba ne ko kuma na karshe ko kuma ko Kavanaugh zai samu zabe, amma kuma yadda 'yan Republican suka bi da lamarin da kuma yadda suka bi da Ford", in ji Guy Cecil, daraktan Priorities USA, wani rukuni da ke taimakawa wajen zaben 'yan Democrat.
Amma, jama'ar Amirka sun nuna cewa sun rabu a kan wanda za su yarda da shi a kan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, wanda ya fi goyon bayan Kavanaugh.
Wani sabon binciken YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun yi imani da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce sun yi imani da shaidar Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin dari na masu amsa sun ce Kavanaugh ya yi ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin dari suka ce haka ne game da Ford.
Bayan da Flake ya yi wa FBI ta fara bincike kan zargin da Ford ya yi, da kuma aƙalla mai gabatar da kara guda ɗaya, Deborah Ramirez, kamar yadda jaridar The Guardian ta ruwaito.
Ford ta shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa a makon da ya gabata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade a lokacin da ta ke 'yar shekara 17.
Ramirez ya ce wanda aka zaɓa a matsayin babban lauya ya nuna mata al'aurarsa a lokacin da yake halartar liyafa a jami'ar Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro World Wide Web yana shirin kaddamar da sabuwar intanet domin gasa da dandamali na Google da Facebook.
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kaddamar da wani kamfanin da zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin da aka yi wa wannan ƙwararren masanin fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne da ke aiki da dandalin Open Source Solid na Berners-Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanda ke da damar samun takamaiman bayani.
A cikin wata hira da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wa dariya cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Ya kamata mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi, yana magana game da farawa.
"Lokaci na tarihi ya zo".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar dandalin Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar shagon yanar gizo tare da bayanan sirri ko kuma POD.
Za ka iya samun jerin lambobin sadarwa, abubuwan da za ka yi, kalanda, kundin kiɗa, da kuma wasu kayan aiki na sana'a da na mutum.
Kamar Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify suna cikin burauzar yanar gizo ɗaya kuma suna aiki a lokaci ɗaya.
Abu na musamman na shagon yanar gizo na bayanan sirri shine cewa yana da cikakken ikon mai amfani wanda zai iya samun damar abin da ke ciki.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "karfafawa ta sirri ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar shugaban kamfanin, John Bruce, manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da albarkatu, aiyuka da kuma basira don taimakawa wajen samar da dandalin Solid ga kowa.
Yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka da aka ɗauka don aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu fasahar kere kere a duk duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta hanyar amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su tattauna da Facebook da Google ba game da ko za su yi wani canji na gaba daya da zai kawo sauyi a cikin tsarin kasuwancin su na yau da kullum.
"Ba na tambayar su izini".
A wani sakon da ya wallafa a Medium ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa, "Mishin Inrupt shi ne samar da wutar lantarki da kuma samar da tsarin halittu don taimakawa kare mutuncin da ingancin sabuwar hanyar sadarwa da aka gina bisa tsarin Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canja hanyar Intanet sa'ad da ya kafa World Wide Web Consortium a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya sha yin magana sosai game da batun tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
A lokacin da aka kafa Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance wanda ya kafa kuma shugaban World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation da Open Data Institute.
"Ina matukar farin ciki da tunanin sabuwar zamanin ci gaban yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
