Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da garin Palu da kuma garin Donggala a tsibirin Celebes:
Palu shine babban birnin Celebes Central, lardin da ke ƙarshen bakin tekun yammacin tsibirin, wanda aka kiyasta cewa yana da mutane 379,800 a cikin 2017.
A lokacin da aka yi bikin cika shekara 40 da kafuwar wannan ƙungiyar, girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku.
